1 “(F) Must require that lands not be rezoned following the site’s
2 inclusion within the urban growth boundary for a period of:
3 “(i) Thirty years for manufactured dwelling parks; or
4 “(ii) Twenty years for manufactured dwellings or prefabricated
5 structures.”.
